data.description: Very good opportunity 2 story condominium, located in the foothills of the wonderful San Gabriel Mountains. Having the proximity of the wonderful Golf Course, has  2 spacious Bedrooms and 1 Bathroom. The property also offers two parking spaces and an attached storage area. Laundry facilities are easily accessible on-site. The community features amenities such as pools, Laundry room  along with  biking paths. Conveniently located near 210  freeway access,  Is also conveniently located to shop Stores, Banks, Restaurants, MRT station, Azusa Pacific University, Citrus College.
